#CircuitBreakerSG D-27
My lazy Sunday #dinner... 蒸简单，蒸好吃，蒸健康 😁

We're having 3 steam dishes tonight 🙈
🐠 Steamed Threadfin with Garlic & Bean Paste
🥬 Steamed Okra topped with Bonito Flakes
🍳 Steamed Trio Eggs

Stay home, stay healthy!

P.s. You may check out my steamed egg recipe here #yvonnemsteamedegg if you're interested 🤗

@ta.dolly Thanks Dolly, you may check out my steamed egg recipe here #yvonnemsteamedegg
@yvonnemsw ok. Thanks Yvonne 👍🙏 Will try out someday 😘
Your steam eggs looked so perfect and delicious. How do you cook it? Can share your recipe?
The steamed eggs look so dreamy 🤤🤤😍
@auntie2beauty_coachnovem I buy whatever available and adjust accordingly.
Which type of bsna paste to buy is nicer? 😊
Threadfin is a very good fish!
@joy_joy11 My lazy meal Oil free kitchen, just need to wash steamer 😆
@ahkuakitchen Yes, Charlene! Grease free & less washing 😆
Nice ! Grease free kitchen 😂 the garlicky bean paste very appetising
My lazy dinner is tabao!! 😆 All looking so delicious n nutritious, your family is so blessed!! 😍

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
Yvonne, I think it’s a great deal to cook. I was attracted to all your dishes and don’t seem like a ‘lazy’ meal at all. 😋😋👍
@fatdough13 Tried this at a Japanese restaurant
Loving the bonito touch on the okra.
Threadfin with garlic and bean paste sounds yummy. I shall try this recipe. Have always been steaming fish with ginger, salt and pepper.
@cookwithsusan Unfortunately... too healthy for the family 😆
